      h3 Column clearing
      p Clear floats at specific breakpoints to prevent awkward wrapping with uneven content.
      .row
        .col-xs-6.col-sm-3 .col-xs-6 .col-sm-3
        .col-xs-6.col-sm-3 .col-xs-6 .col-sm-3

